# Design Language

Modern SaaS — minimal, fast, premium.

## References (inspiration, not copy)
- Layout: Linear
- Sidebar: Discord / Notion
- Table: CardTrader
- Dashboard: Vercel
- Animations: Arc Browser (150ms transitions, hover everywhere)
- Theme: Obsidian dark default (#1e1e1e range, blue accent)

## Rules
- Rounded corners, soft shadows, large spacing, neutral colors
- Glassmorphism only where appropriate
- No ugly HTML tables — use virtualized div rows
- Premium empty states with icon + headline + CTA
- Desktop first, responsive, accessibility compliant
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`
